candidates.title: Refacto/db tables and ttl
candidates.body:
## Proposed Changes

- Remove Interactions and Path  db tables 
- add new low_data mode which don't save messages in db
- add ttl for Conversations, Messages, Memory and State
    - add new event values ttl: i64, low_data: bool
    - add new env values TTL: String, LOW_DATA: String
- add new endpoint 'data/cleanup'  which delete all the expired data (only useful for postgresql)
